rows.label: qst501301_msg0001
rows.name: Mo-mo... This not good at all...

rows.label: qst501301_msg0002
rows.name:
What should Rentarenta do
with empty warehouse?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0003
rows.name:
If nobody use, better to
give to someone for free...

rows.label: qst501301_msg0004
rows.name: Mo-mo?!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0005
rows.name: You people Drivers and Blades?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0006
qst501301_msg0007
rows.name: But!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0008
rows.name:
Maybe some Blades of friends
want extra space to use?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0009
rows.name:
Wanting bookcases maybe,
or just place to store
lots of favorite stuff?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0010
rows.name:
If Drivers willing, me rent out
lovely warehouse to Driver friends!
Low low price of 100,000G!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0011
rows.name:
Didn't I just hear you saying
something about "free"...?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0012
rows.name:
I could've sworn I heard
you say something about
giving it away for free.

rows.label: qst501301_msg0013
rows.name:
That is quite the bold offer. Were
you not muttering about giving it
away for free a few moments ago?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0014
rows.name:
You greedy little fluffball.
I heard you saying you'd give
it away for free just now!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0015
rows.name:
Rentarenta true Nopon. Very
determine to turn useless
warehouse into money.

rows.label: qst501301_msg0016
rows.name:
W-well, if friends find way into
warehouse without opening door, by
all means use to heart's content.

rows.label: qst501301_msg0017
rows.name:
But if friends pay 100,000G, me open
door and friends can use freely!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0028
rows.name: Pay

rows.label: qst501301_msg0029
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: qst501301_msg0019
rows.name: Thanks much to friends!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0020
rows.name:
Warehouse and Dad both more
happy-happy if somebody make
use of wasted space.

rows.label: qst501301_msg0021
rows.name:
And Rentarenta more happy-happy
now a little bit more rich!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0022
rows.name:
Rentarenta leave door open, so
friends use freely from now on!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0023
rows.name: Bye-bye now!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0024
rows.name: Hm? Too pricey?

rows.label: qst501301_msg0025
rows.name:
Then Rentarenta make
slightly better offer!

rows.label: qst501301_msg0026
rows.name:
Rentarenta can not make any
better offer than this.

rows.label: qst501301_msg0027
rows.name:
If friends change mind, come
back see Rentarenta any time!
